data.description: Prepare to be charmed by this fantastic 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom gem on a oversized corner lot, nestled in the heart of Carrollwood. What's more, this property includes a standalone guest suite that could serve as an Airbnb rental or an ideal space for guests. As you step inside the main house, you'll find an open, welcoming living space, perfect for everyday living and entertaining. The kitchen is a chef's dream, with modern stainless steel appliance, granite countertops, stone backsplash, solid wood cabinets, 42 inch upper cabinets, plenty of counterspace with a peninsula that has seating space for those quick breakfasts. This home has room for everyone! The main home has four bedrooms offering space and comfort, and the master suite is a true retreat with a spa-like bathroom. The home features hand scraped wood floors throughout the first level and stair case. Ceramic tile in all the wet areas, a wood burning fireplace in the living room, a huge storage area under the staircase. Head outside to discover your own private oasis with a screened lanai overlooking a sparkling pool. A huge yard, plenty of landscaping, a recycled sprinkler system, two separate screened in patios make it an ideal for fun gatherings or just soaking up the Florida sun. The standalone guest suite is a versatile space with its own bathroom, offering the potential for an Airbnb rental income, a cozy home office, or a private retreat for guests. The roof is ONLY 10 years old! Best of all, there is no HOA OR CDD FEE! Carrollwood offers top-rated schools, great shopping, and a vibrant community atmosphere, all just a short drive from downtown Tampa. Don't miss your chance to make this amazing home with a separate guest suite yours. Schedule a viewing today before it's gone! Walk-through 3d tour at https://bit.ly/13811capitoldrtour
